Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.51,0:01:35.44,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今　感じてる　手を伸ばしたら
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.55,0:01:40.42,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空　高くきらめく流星
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.80,0:01:45.74,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ずっと追い掛けて　何度転んでも
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.10,0:01:50.89,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,もう止められない衝動なんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.57,0:01:56.28,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夜空にボクたちのstory
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.72,0:02:02.57,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最初の1ページめくり　動き出す！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.94,0:02:05.47,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巡り巡るミライへと
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.80,0:02:08.10,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ボクら今駆け出して
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.29,0:02:11.33,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,何十億年先へ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.56,0:02:13.16,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,届くように
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.50,0:02:15.80,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遥か彼方の空へ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.14,0:02:19.76,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,映す夢のカケラを掴んで
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.07,0:02:24.63,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,静寂の闇さえ射抜くよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.01,0:02:27.96,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,強く願うんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.23,0:02:32.58,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Just!Never say Never
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.51,0:01:35.44,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在 我能感觉到 只要伸出双手
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.55,0:01:40.42,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就能够到 遥远夜空中夺目的流星
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.80,0:01:45.74,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直紧追不舍 就算一次次跌倒
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.10,0:01:50.89,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这份心中的冲动也无法平息
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.57,0:01:56.28,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将我们的故事寄于夜空
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.72,0:02:02.57,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翻过那最初的1页 开始行动！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.94,0:02:05.47,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朝着辗转轮回的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.80,0:02:08.10,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在我们冲了出去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.29,0:02:11.33,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了能够到达
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.56,0:02:13.16,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那几十亿年后的前方
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.50,0:02:15.80,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朝着遥远尽头的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.14,0:02:19.76,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紧握手中映着梦想的碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.07,0:02:24.63,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将那寂静的黑暗也射穿
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.01,0:02:27.96,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用心祈愿
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.23,0:02:32.58,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永不言弃
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.26,0:22:31.40,ED_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,やがて悪夢に支配された　闇さえ光が射す
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.20,0:22:40.84,ED_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知らず知らずに　引き寄せ合う　汚れを知らぬ魂
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.04,0:22:46.28,ED_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,何を　信じればいい
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.14,0:22:52.09,ED_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,何処へ　流されて行けばいい
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.09,0:22:57.06,ED_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,いつかこの手に　安らぎの時間
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.06,0:23:01.55,ED_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,屈辱にさえ魅了された未来
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.55,0:23:07.20,ED_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那が動き出す　悲しみは加速する
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.70,0:23:11.64,ED_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閉ざされた心を　貫くように
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.05,0:23:18.08,ED_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永遠が生まれる　宿命に操られ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.45,0:23:22.86,ED_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,涙を重ねて　Somebody to love
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.93,0:00:00.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.26,0:22:31.40,ED_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受恶梦支配的黑暗 最终也迎来了光芒的照射
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.20,0:22:40.84,ED_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无垢的灵魂 在不知不觉间 相互吸引
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.04,0:22:46.28,ED_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底 该去相信什么
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.14,0:22:52.09,ED_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底 流落至何处才是尽头
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.09,0:22:57.06,ED_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终有一日 要用这双手获得安宁片刻
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.06,0:23:01.55,ED_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未来甚至为屈辱迷失
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.55,0:23:07.20,ED_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始转动的刹那 不断加速的悲伤
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.70,0:23:11.64,ED_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宛如要将那紧闭的心贯穿
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.05,0:23:18.08,ED_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在永远所生出的宿命的操纵下
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.45,0:23:22.86,ED_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不断落泪 Somebody to love
Dialogue: 0,0:00:-9.00,0:00:-9.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.25,0:00:09.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好咧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.25,0:00:26.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.53,0:00:27.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.18,0:00:30.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…等等
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.85,0:00:33.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 便当便当
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.14,0:00:35.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等下啦 岛津
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.94,0:00:41.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,写作“真名” 读作MANA
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.45,0:00:47.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若被对方知道真名 就会受到支配 必须服从其命令
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.04,0:00:53.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那什么…我只是…那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.56,0:00:55.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,便当…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.65,0:00:59.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我拿就是了 拿还不行吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.27,0:01:07.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正我已经无法违抗你了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.20,0:01:08.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.46,0:02:47.51,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(956,560)}{\fad(550,0)}第六话 约定
Dialogue: 0,0:00:-9.00,0:00:-9.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.40,0:02:45.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我去买下面包很快就回来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.78,0:02:47.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.55,0:02:57.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,头疼了啊 自那以来和岛津一直关系很僵
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.40,0:03:00.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白她不想被人知道真名的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.22,0:03:03.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也知道她因此深受打击
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.03,0:03:06.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但为何会那么地…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.17,0:03:09.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朔邪 你打算在哪吃？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.63,0:03:12.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？浅野君
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.62,0:03:14.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.98,0:03:15.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.50,0:03:17.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.42,0:03:22.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说 朔邪？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.05,0:03:26.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.79,0:03:29.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.76,0:03:33.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.97,0:03:36.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朔邪是在害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.19,0:03:38.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怕我吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.17,0:03:39.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.33,0:03:44.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怕的是可能会失去当家之位这件事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.67,0:03:46.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她？为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.15,0:03:51.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被知道真名之人会绝对服从对方
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.79,0:03:54.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能会把那种人奉为当家不是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.28,0:03:58.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,立即将其革职是岛津家的规矩
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.95,0:04:00.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…因为我…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.47,0:04:04.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最终虽然是由首领来定夺
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.55,0:04:09.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过如果有个万一 朔邪就拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.70,0:04:11.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为那孩子是孤身一人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.85,0:04:13.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孤身一人？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.26,0:04:17.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不曾考虑过
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.77,0:04:21.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么那家伙是一个人生活
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.49,0:04:26.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来一次都没听她提起过父母的事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.52,0:04:28.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.05,0:04:31.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真一郎 欢迎回来！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.77,0:04:35.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 让我好等啊喵 真一郎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.77,0:04:37.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我肚子饿了喵 真一郎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.85,0:04:40.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你为什么光着身子啊 衣服呢衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.97,0:04:42.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿着憋屈嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.57,0:04:43.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你啊你…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.34,0:04:47.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊不是的 这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.45,0:04:49.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咋的 有意见？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.09,0:04:56.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉好吓人啊喵
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.41,0:04:58.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该怎么办才好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.42,0:05:07.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你很在意吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.90,0:05:10.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亏她还一直躲着你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.67,0:05:12.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.73,0:05:15.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你强吻她吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.59,0:05:17.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接吻？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.34,0:05:18.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说是接吻呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.39,0:05:23.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时如果真一郎大人没有那么做
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.94,0:05:25.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们俩就都死了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.69,0:05:27.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话是如此…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.60,0:05:31.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对于那样冷淡的姐姐 不应该已经对她断念了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.55,0:05:36.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真一郎大人 还请赐予我力量
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.83,0:05:38.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朔邪姐姐她已经…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.76,0:05:45.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙不是会因为这点事就放弃的人 你也明白的吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.28,0:05:49.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就知道您会这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.55,0:05:50.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.03,0:05:53.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不愿意以这种形式当上当家
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.15,0:05:58.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐就麻烦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.35,0:06:01.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她已经一副赢得天下的样子了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.24,0:06:04.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙雾大人也真是让人困扰呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.67,0:06:08.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嚯？你不也是推崇须世璃的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.27,0:06:13.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正式决定应该等等二人成人 而且…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.16,0:06:17.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呵呵 行了 交给我吧 那我挂了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.93,0:06:25.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馆主 到时辰了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.51,0:06:42.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来 就岛津朔邪的处置方式 进行众议
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.18,0:06:51.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你为什么要跟着我啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.96,0:06:55.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是回同一个家这不是没办法的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.43,0:06:57.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.11,0:06:59.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好疼…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.39,0:07:01.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要逞强啦 来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.74,0:07:12.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我感到很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.36,0:07:15.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你带我来是为了说这个？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.87,0:07:19.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我听说了 因为我你可能会失去当家之位
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.10,0:07:21.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.91,0:07:24.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当时我一心只想救你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.86,0:07:27.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且也不知道有这回事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.14,0:07:33.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道你如此执着于当家之位的原因
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.20,0:07:38.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是就结果而言我做了违背你意愿的事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.44,0:07:40.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.34,0:07:51.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看到了什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.62,0:07:53.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.85,0:07:56.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,读取真名的时候 没看到什么吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.04,0:08:01.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…说起来 我看到你躺在陈旧的屋内
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.32,0:08:03.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多只有幼儿园大小的岁数
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.63,0:08:07.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后 某个人给你了那个布偶
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.41,0:08:08.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.76,0:08:11.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我不是很明白
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.08,0:08:12.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.97,0:08:18.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我曾经很喜欢能看见海的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.62,0:08:19.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.64,0:08:22.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我的父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.80,0:08:23.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.78,0:08:26.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 总是像这样看着海
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.04,0:08:35.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说…为什么不一起生活呢？也在镰仓吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.66,0:08:36.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不在
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.35,0:08:41.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲也好母亲也好 八年前就失踪杳无音讯了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.74,0:08:49.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,八年前 他们二人前去与妖魔战斗 就再也没回来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.49,0:08:53.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本应和他们同行的抚子还有奶奶都浑身是伤
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.80,0:08:55.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不肯告诉我到底发生了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.69,0:08:57.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不仅如此
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.76,0:09:03.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自那之后我的父母 在岛津家就被视作禁忌闭口不提
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.72,0:09:05.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就好像什么都没发生过似的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.25,0:09:07.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.55,0:09:11.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我的父亲是西洋魔术师
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.96,0:09:17.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对岛津家而言 让外人加入族内是很少见的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.12,0:09:22.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为灵力的强弱和素质基本都靠遗传
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.20,0:09:26.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 也有像你这样的例外就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.37,0:09:29.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了将继承的力量进一步提高
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.13,0:09:32.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只在族内反反复复进行婚事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.98,0:09:36.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这样作为日本首屈一指的灵能力者一族
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.30,0:09:38.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,几百年来一直称霸着
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.68,0:09:44.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西洋魔术师加入这样的家族 你能想象遭到多少反对吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.00,0:09:46.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我大概…可以想象…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.30,0:09:49.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比你想象得更甚！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.34,0:09:53.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲自不用说 连结婚对象的母亲也被忌讳
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.25,0:09:58.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 更甚至是自二人诞生的我也…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.03,0:10:00.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个女孩的血是肮脏的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.58,0:10:03.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是历史悠远的传统的污点
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.72,0:10:07.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定会带来灾难的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.19,0:10:08.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 多么不祥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.13,0:10:10.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是她没生下来就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.94,0:10:13.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁都不肯我告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.50,0:10:18.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父母发生了什么 是否还活着都不告诉我！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.20,0:10:21.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我无论如何都想知道！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.65,0:10:26.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然她们要隐瞒真相 那我就自己当上当家
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.71,0:10:28.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是才这样…吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.63,0:10:33.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要当上了岛津家的当家
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.48,0:10:35.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就能让他们统统闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.16,0:10:38.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靠实力让那群人认可我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.96,0:10:42.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后我一定要找到父亲和母亲！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:-9.00,0:00:-9.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.91,0:10:51.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.83,0:10:53.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.68,0:10:54.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才送到的喵
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.39,0:10:56.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁寄来的？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.96,0:10:59.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.04,0:11:03.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时春？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.63,0:11:08.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,镜子？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.79,0:11:10.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有相当年代了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.15,0:11:21.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真一郎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.95,0:11:24.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真一郎！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.09,0:11:32.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.85,0:11:34.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被吞进去了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.43,0:11:35.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被那面镜子？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.11,0:11:37.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大意了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.61,0:11:42.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是本家的屋子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.22,0:11:49.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人来了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.59,0:11:56.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,认识吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.91,0:12:00.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.70,0:12:03.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.75,0:12:06.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲 母亲！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.16,0:12:13.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你 你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.38,0:12:16.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会让你再出手了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.12,0:12:21.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲母亲由我来保护
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.16,0:12:25.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是云外镜…呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.07,0:12:27.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是啥？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.29,0:12:32.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是从被镜子吸入的猎物身上 挖掘出负面感情
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.72,0:12:34.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玩弄人心的妖魔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.33,0:12:38.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牺牲者精神被破坏 最终…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.50,0:12:40.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会！真一郎！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.83,0:12:41.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.41,0:12:42.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玉子小姐！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.62,0:12:44.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们干什么喵！真一郎他！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.49,0:12:47.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弄坏了镜子 他们俩就回不来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.07,0:12:47.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不快点的话很危险...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.73,0:12:48.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎！？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.22,0:12:50.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃出的方法只有一个
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.75,0:12:55.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在镜子里打倒身为罪魁祸首的云外镜
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.17,0:12:57.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,岛津！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.84,0:13:01.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能过来！会被波及的！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.52,0:13:07.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,岛津的人从我身边夺走了父亲和母亲 不可原谅！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.89,0:13:08.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唔！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.06,0:13:09.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都牟羽！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.48,0:13:16.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都牟刈！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.15,0:13:21.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都牟刈！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.05,0:13:27.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会输给你这种人的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.40,0:13:33.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,输给忘记父亲母亲 光惦记着成为岛津当家的你这种人！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.10,0:13:38.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的 我是为了寻找父母亲才想成为岛津当家…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.21,0:13:38.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗人！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.54,0:13:43.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你只是想对忌讳你的那群人还以颜色
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.90,0:13:45.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不是的！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.01,0:13:45.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗子！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.48,0:13:58.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事 这里是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.90,0:14:02.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲！母亲！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.06,0:14:04.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 不要走！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.12,0:14:08.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好过分 好过分啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.52,0:14:12.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把父亲母亲还给我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.37,0:14:15.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种…是幻觉…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.97,0:14:17.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个女孩的血是肮脏的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.47,0:14:19.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 多么不祥
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.91,0:14:21.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是她没生下来就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.87,0:14:22.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啰嗦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.53,0:14:25.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啰嗦 啰嗦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.04,0:14:30.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是我当上了当家 那群家伙…那群家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.43,0:14:33.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全都杀掉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.96,0:14:36.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不对
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.65,0:14:40.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那群家伙拆散了我的家人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.54,0:14:47.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咒骂父亲轻蔑母亲 还忌讳我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.93,0:14:52.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是没办法的吗 我非常不甘心非常伤心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.50,0:14:56.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可原谅 一定要当上当家还以颜色
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.76,0:14:57.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.02,0:15:00.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,岛津什么的看我统统毁掉！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.59,0:15:01.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住口！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.03,0:15:04.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是你的心里话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.01,0:15:09.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向令自己一家不幸的岛津一族进行复仇
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.85,0:15:13.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是你成为当家的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.16,0:15:14.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.91,0:15:19.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是刚从你自己的嘴里听到了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.37,0:15:24.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在心底激荡回旋 漆黑污秽的 朝向岛津一族的怒号
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.10,0:15:25.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啰 啰嗦！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.05,0:15:27.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看来跟你很合得来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.48,0:15:31.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不被任何人祝福的岛津家的姑娘
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.68,0:15:33.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闭嘴！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.53,0:15:44.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.37,0:15:45.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,振作点 岛津
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.35,0:15:47.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,岛津
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.18,0:15:45.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.53,0:15:49.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的 不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.01,0:15:50.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.50,0:16:01.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们都是自出生的一刻起就被人忌讳的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.11,0:16:02.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,岛津一族的黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.04,0:16:04.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.88,0:16:07.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 就去死吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.09,0:16:15.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧 岛津？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.37,0:16:16.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,离远点！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.07,0:16:20.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梓弓 檀弓 槻弓 互相吸引
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.78,0:16:23.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放矢复归 恭送众神
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.04,0:16:26.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,岛津流弓灵术奥义
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.99,0:16:30.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羽羽斩！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.12,0:16:37.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,岛津！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.24,0:16:42.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,够了 别打了！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.41,0:16:44.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想看的这种战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.92,0:16:49.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有比这更让人愉快的好戏看了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.48,0:16:51.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同为岛津之人 互相厮杀吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.14,0:16:54.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么？为什么要做到这个地步！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.04,0:16:59.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然是因为憎恨 恨杀了我的岛津
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.30,0:17:01.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀了你？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.41,0:17:03.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无法原谅
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.00,0:17:08.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要得救的话 就要两人合二为一
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.51,0:17:09.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,合二为一？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.29,0:17:13.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接受存在于心底的憎恨
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.87,0:17:16.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想对岛津家复仇对吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.78,0:17:18.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就去复仇不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.07,0:17:24.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很简单 本来就是在你心中的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.55,0:17:25.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老老实实接受吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.70,0:17:28.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了什么在战斗着？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.48,0:17:33.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不惜忍受着这么痛苦这么悲伤的心情是为何？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.07,0:17:34.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是为了谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.52,0:17:37.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.56,0:17:41.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来得到解脱吧 你就是我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.80,0:17:43.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.22,0:17:48.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧 一起保护父亲母亲吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.40,0:17:50.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从可憎的岛津手中
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.19,0:18:01.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行！这家伙不是你！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.40,0:18:03.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真一郎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.35,0:18:07.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道年幼的你有怎样的回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.40,0:18:11.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想必非常不甘 非常的难过
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.14,0:18:15.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是现在的你和那时不同了不是吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.88,0:18:20.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我所知道的岛津任性 好强 傲慢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.90,0:18:25.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但不是会被憎恨支配了心智的软弱家伙！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.86,0:18:27.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啰嗦闭嘴！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.72,0:18:35.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是为了寻找自己父母亲才在战斗的吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.26,0:18:37.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会跟你一起找的！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.34,0:18:39.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 不要输给她！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.03,0:18:42.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真一郎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.24,0:18:46.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 现在的我已经今非昔比
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.53,0:18:49.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在的我有着…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.62,0:18:53.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.33,0:18:58.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真一郎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.63,0:19:02.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,岛津 这家伙的真名叫红水仙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.61,0:19:03.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.79,0:19:04.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到此为止了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.11,0:19:05.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,红水仙！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.20,0:19:09.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住 住手
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.54,0:19:15.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安心沉睡吧 我已经很明白你的心情了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.57,0:19:17.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然如此
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.84,0:19:20.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 已经够了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.64,0:19:25.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经…够了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.02,0:19:28.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是愚蠢的姑娘
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.22,0:19:30.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永别了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.69,0:19:43.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,镜 镜子！？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.72,0:19:45.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真 真一郎呢！？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.27,0:19:52.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来得救了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.03,0:19:56.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被弹到奇怪的地方来了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.09,0:20:00.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之能回来就很好了不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.59,0:20:02.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次我还真以为要怎么样了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.01,0:20:06.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过让那女人逃掉了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.65,0:20:07.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有下次的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.50,0:20:11.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 说实话不想再见到她了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.58,0:20:17.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,岛津？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.42,0:20:26.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪 为什么 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.65,0:20:31.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 好奇怪…我 明明一点都不觉得伤心…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.10,0:20:39.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的 我说过的吧？我会和你一起寻找父母亲的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.42,0:20:41.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.98,0:20:45.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 一起找吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.48,0:20:48.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 约好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.72,0:21:05.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天晚饭你想吃什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.81,0:21:06.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱尔兰炖菜
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.19,0:21:08.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 又来？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.92,0:21:10.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就要爱尔兰炖菜！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.89,0:21:12.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 好难做的…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.27,0:21:15.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到找到父母亲之前 一直都要！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.35,0:21:21.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真没辙啊 那今晚就用羊肉挑战下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.71,0:21:24.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我陪你去买食材 走吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.37,0:21:25.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 喂？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.46,0:21:27.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天是特例！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.08,0:21:29.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.58,0:21:33.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说…刚才啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.02,0:21:35.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 我知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.27,0:21:38.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你哭过这事 是我们俩的秘密 对吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.52,0:21:43.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别再说了啦 笨蛋笨蛋笨蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.68,0:21:42.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,疼疼疼疼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.03,0:21:44.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道啦 知道啦岛津
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.30,0:21:48.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫我朔邪就好啦 讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.43,0:21:48.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.63,0:21:53.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毕竟真名都让你知道了 都事到如今了 真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.34,0:21:58.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了啦 朔邪
